"You've come to the right place!  Here!  If you've got the gold, I've got the drink!"  The Peddler takes your gold and fills the flask, handing it back to you with a secretive wink.  "I'm off to deal with the Hell Elves.  Don't get me wrong, they're good people...so long as you're real respectfull like...and don't mind the sun..."  The Peddler trundles off.
